Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}終わらない懺悔と憂鬱の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}完全な自分がどこにもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}最低な自分しか見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:01.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为就是做不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}说着不该是这样的 逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又想要一了百了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:17.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}封闭自己自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}受伤 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便抱着迷路羔羊的感情入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}后悔也完全完全完全无法释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:30.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}独自不断的钻着牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}理想总是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只准备好自责的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:44.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}寻求着那廉价的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}虚心接受屡教不改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}昧着良心得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有尽头的忏悔与忧郁的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有完美的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只有最差劲的自己
Comment: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,========================ED==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}始まりはただの恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}気づけば唯一無二の拠り所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}同じ時刻み　齢をとろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}これからは　お願いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}so long time 隣りにいて　永久に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}闘いの日々に疲れても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}怒りの雨に降られても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}濡れてしまうならば迷わず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}俺が代わりにあなたの傘となる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}寒くないよ　隣にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}ただそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}その笑顔にまた癒やされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}世界中　探しても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}代わりなんていない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}そこにいるだけでまた満たされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}どんなに傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}この身捧げ守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}最初不过是单纯的小小恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不觉间却成了我唯一的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}让我们在岁月中一同刻下年华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}今后也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}so long time 永远在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不论是历战的疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}还是暴风雨的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}当你脆弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我将毫不犹豫地为你遮风挡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}只要你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就不会感到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}总能被你的微笑治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就算寻遍整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}也没有谁能代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}在你身边就是我最大的满足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不管受怎样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我都将舍身相护
